    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home a fantastic vehicle that's been well-loved and is ready for many more miles! This car is in solid, good condition, offering a smooth ride and dependable performance that you can count on. It\u2019s been well-maintained and is clean and comfortable, making it a perfect choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car with plenty of life left!",
